fiftyone.mobile.detection.entities.stream

Interface ICacheList

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FixedCacheList, StreamCacheList, StreamVariableList

    public interface ICacheList
    Lists that use a cache can return information about the cache misses for performance analysis. They implement this interface to provide this data to the DataSet.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      double getPercentageMisses()
      Returns the percentage of cache misses.
      long getSwitches()
      The number of times the lists have been switched.
      void resetCache()
      Resets the cache used by the list.
